  "body": "<div class=\"se-main-container\">\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-b5482499-1260-47e1-bdee-633b12438394\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-09da7dbd-e858-4ef7-9bfb-59c75b1864a3\"><span style=\"color:#666666;background-color:#ffffff;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic  se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-58714BE6-AE6E-45A6-A412-B34C2041BF55\">이상기후 때문인지, 전 세계가 유래없는 기상이변을 경험하고 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-ea0329e3-7679-4e4b-bf98-3f9072094735\"><span style=\"color:#666666;background-color:#ffffff;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic  se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-74F33099-B8FC-4FE6-ABFF-DFE009FD042B\">이번 여름 외국은 40도가 넘는 폭염에 시달리는 곳이 많다죠? </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-5cdd53fb-6907-487a-bf8b-126678473208\"><span style=\"color:#666666;background-color:#ffffff;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic  se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-05FFE110-AEE7-43C5-BFBB-2D26D281F63E\">우리나라도 장마철이 끝나면  올 여름 많이 더울 것으로 예상됩니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-F08022DD-A169-4674-AC47-7945D88372F4\"><span style=\"color:#666666;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic  se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-C8C2055F-C53B-4B7F-BF7E-54C4DF6F766E\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-85016ff6-99c8-4500-a1a0-996d52691f1e\"><span style=\"color:#666666;background-color:#ffffff;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic  se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-41B10252-11B2-4AE2-9FBD-F0CB37822764\">이렇게 무더위에 지칠 땐 </span><span style=\"color:#00a84b;background-color:#ffffff;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic  se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-F963C573-9E8B-4A48-91D5-F06CC4319659\"><b>&#x27;생맥산&#x27;</b></span><span style=\"color:#666666;background-color:#ffffff;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic  se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-9DC29D4F-A36A-47B9-A705-34D118B040F3\">으로 기력을 보강하면</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-1616523c-f83c-4834-b5ca-d40d235634fc\"><span style=\"color:#666666;background-color:#ffffff;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic  se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-4BAEF1B0-D729-4D87-AAC1-975680C98408\">더위를 이겨낼 수 있답니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-8D5DDB31-CB76-42D5-8C00-3B92F39EE900\"><span style=\"color:#666666;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic  se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-AB4AAE60-FB0F-48B7-802C-080B290743D8\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-f8b66eb9-6b02-4abd-9d87-2322f81d0a88\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-left\" >\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-f8b66eb9-6b02-4abd-9d87-2322f81d0a88\", \"src\" : \"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/MjAyMzA4MDRfNDkg/MDAxNjkxMTM3MzY1NjM1.wshF_DLq8J0H3c-7vwOPrpp73OA7qzSxucXQpwGjUY0g.SKlROzPBgoGjdGSyhsyoknNAHQBgTafCC6_7uJtkSlcg.JPEG.isuhani/beach-g08b9e9f74_1280.jpg\", \"originalWidth\" : \"1280\", \"originalHeight\" : \"720\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/MjAyMzA4MDRfNDkg/MDAxNjkxMTM3MzY1NjM1.wshF_DLq8J0H3c-7vwOPrpp73OA7qzSxucXQpwGjUY0g.SKlROzPBgoGjdGSyhsyoknNAHQBgTafCC6_7uJtkSlcg.JPEG.isuhani/beach-g08b9e9f74_1280.jpg?type=w80_blur\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/MjAyMzA4MDRfNDkg/MDAxNjkxMTM3MzY1NjM1.wshF_DLq8J0H3c-7vwOPrpp73OA7qzSxucXQpwGjUY0g.SKlROzPBgoGjdGSyhsyoknNAHQBgTafCC6_7uJtkSlcg.JPEG.isuhani/beach-g08b9e9f74_1280.jpg?type=w580\" data-width=\"500\" data-height=\"281\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-5efd92a9-e4bb-4082-bd52-e788c6308fe6\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-123DA6E3-409D-4EC5-B7C3-37F713DAAD43\"><span style=\"color:#666666;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic  se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-27BBF061-4A34-4E29-8F95-BF1B5C7C80D6\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-a15eaa39-658a-4193-8c16-8e41fd4443fb\"><span style=\"color:#666666;background-color:#ffffff;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic  se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-1B452C8C-075A-463C-B3BD-A2F7F2C5A22C\">흔히 더위 먹는다고 표현하죠. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-810433ee-f769-4516-9277-dbced1a1cbff\"><span style=\"color:#666666;background-color:#ffffff;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic  se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-A1B8B92B-D76C-4448-A22D-E8F61B30589A\">더위를 먹는다는 것은</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-d19bd088-e1db-41f2-b67a-fe1fba368357\"><span style=\"color:#666666;background-color:#ffffff;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic  se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-0EAEFB9D-5A1B-4282-92BF-0253D7729125\">한의학에서 말하는 &#x27;</span><span style=\"color:#666666;background-color:#ffffff;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-FEED6956-A945-409C-936A-AC0ADD8B9D52\">주하병(注夏病)</span><span style=\"color:#666666;background-color:#ffffff;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic  se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-962090EC-2A19-4C1D-AD78-A62986C41E45\">&#x27;과 &#x27;서병(暑病)&#x27;을 일컫습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-B7232860-27E9-4886-80B3-01CF574DF80A\"><span style=\"color:#666666;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic  se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-8BB833A9-53FC-4986-AD92-DB7E90F79BDC\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-0475f422-069e-4e07-b8d6-60a06ca2de7f\"><span style=\"color:#00a84b;background-color:#ffffff;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic  se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-D416E0B3-C1B4-476F-BDE4-82772ACADD9D\"><b>주하병(注夏病)</b></span><span style=\"color:#666666;background-color:#ffffff;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic  se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-5DABC37C-8C7C-4CB0-AB76-4616D2E58DC6\">은</span><span style=\"color:#666666;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic  se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-247A73D0-B830-45A2-B5E0-6BFBDF728764\"><b> 무더위 때문에 속이 메슥거리고 입이 쓰면서 입안이 마르는 증상</b></span><span style=\"color:#666666;background-color:#ffffff;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic  se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-B46276BA-49DC-4A7F-9A0F-87C2093B8F13\">이 타나납니다. 정신이 피로하고 자주 졸리며, 먹는 것이 줄어들고 몸이 무력해지는 등의 증상도 동반됩니다. 매년 여름 무렵이 되면 몸이 힘들고 여름을 탄다는 분들이 이에 해당합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-6055DA82-17B0-45E3-A2B4-081BBE04D52D\"><span style=\"color:#666666;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic  se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-23747172-4B8C-4CA4-9141-5D6F2EACCDE8\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-7764d5ed-22fc-4a16-b6b4-e8b100b89450\"><span style=\"color:#666666;background-color:#ffffff;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic  se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-BAA58826-70E9-4A48-B7BD-6B160766C2C1\">이럴 때! 생맥산이 안성맞춤이죠 :)</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-F6CEF0DE-63CB-44A8-B9F7-26BD1539BCB4\"><span style=\"color:#666666;\" class=\"se-fs-fs11 se-ff-nanumgothic  se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-CEFBCEFD-F9DF-4DE0-AA64-FDB0CC560AA1\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-e2620fcd-f8e6-4952-a01d-b7013270eea2\"><span style=\"color:#00a84b;background-color:#ffffff;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic  se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-D2231693-F675-4726-B9BE-E357536B226D\"><b> 서병(暑病)</b></span><span style=\"color:#666666;background-color:#ffffff;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic  se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-1CEEF0F1-B3B4-4524-AAA9-FD5C9C30F3C4\">은 </span><span style=\"color:#666666;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic  se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-8C4CBA51-2BDC-4B6F-AC86-12550D142843\"><b>한여름 푹푹 찌는 무더위의 시기에 몸이 상하는 것</b></span><span style=\"color:#666666;background-color:#ffffff;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic  se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-6FF2FDB9-9971-4A6F-AB2D-6BE3273A2627\">을 일컫습니다. 무척 더운 날 야외에서 활동을 하거나 일을 하다가 더위를 먹은 경우 이에 해당됩니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-80A53075-C090-4FBD-B549-B8F0325D5FB1\"><span style=\"color:#666666;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic  se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-14A11422-B5DA-4DBF-AA8E-CF6028E15E45\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-c6334aad-8516-4f44-951d-7b393c454a34\"><span style=\"color:#666666;background-color:#ffffff;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic  se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-94272C00-ABBF-464F-9C61-708C89C69AF5\"> </span><span style=\"color:#666666;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic  se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-26531782-F147-44A5-A39D-3517283156F9\"><b>머리가 아프고 몸에 열이 나며, 입이 마르고 가슴이 답답하면서 식은땀이 흐르는 증상을 호소하는 것</b></span><span style=\"color:#666666;background-color:#ffffff;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic  se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-F3100BF1-D4FA-4C03-9DF4-AEFE1468A44B\">을 </span><span style=\"color:#00a84b;background-color:#ffffff;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic  se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-10A7ADB2-CB1D-4142-81BE-01FA653AD010\"><b>양서(陽暑)</b></span><span style=\"color:#666666;background-color:#ffffff;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic  se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-0F77255E-BE15-4BFE-B708-FD6FD8E30D5B\">라 합니다. 이때는 현기증이 나면서 쓰러질 수도 있기 때문에 </span><span style=\"color:#666666;background-color:#ffffff;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic  se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-FB4D1D84-9CA0-4AD4-A918-005223AD7AD9\"><u>빨리 서늘한 곳으로 옮긴 후 휴식을 취하면서 충분한 수분 공급을 해주어야 합니다.</u></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-FC629D95-1468-4C26-ADA8-57B95922F5AA\"><span style=\"color:#666666;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic  se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-EF764FC9-74E6-4E94-A99F-85BAAA9EC81F\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-2f655a86-0a31-4e63-a947-559611038d9b\"><span style=\"color:#666666;background-color:#ffffff;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic  se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-0DC81444-C1D9-4916-863A-0F21B73CCDD8\">몸에 쌓인 열을 내려주고 진액(몸의 수분)을 보충해줘야 합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-da89b60d-f7e2-4f6d-83a2-d7fd56c304d2\"><span style=\"color:#666666;background-color:#ffffff;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic  se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-0F4F9F82-2665-492C-8037-B89D6B126F5B\">역시나 생맥산이 필요한 상황입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-822736D1-2339-4544-B945-3276105E2934\"><span style=\"color:#666666;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic  se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-1C230525-1111-44FC-8EB7-BD3F0A527A3E\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-aeceb150-c067-4940-9a1f-d8bab0a11a8b\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-left\" >\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-aeceb150-c067-4940-9a1f-d8bab0a11a8b\", \"src\" : \"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/MjAyMzA3MThfNyAg/MDAxNjg5Njc4MDAwNjc2.Z_vwZbR7Sz8KO2aBJaMqhkHivea8z3OQzh-xrcimDisg.gWjELhw1lvOInKUY-xAdOfnYcZO9IHb6E2EwYze110Yg.JPEG.isuhani/%EB%82%A8%EC%84%B1%EC%97%AD_%EC%9D%B4%EC%88%98%ED%95%9C%EC%